# Mac-only helper scripts go here.
#
# The MLC pipeline (convert_weight / gen_config / compile) only runs on Mac
# because Apple Silicon Metal is what the source-built `mlc_llm` package was
# wired against. If you write batch wrappers, build-bootstrap helpers, or
# anything else that automates the runbook in ../README.md, commit them here.
#
# This file exists only to keep the directory tracked by git. Delete it once
# real scripts land.
